
“I felt HAPPY because I saw the others were HAPPY and because I knew I should feel HAPPY, but I wasn’t really HAPPY.”
Roberto Bolano, 2666

Examples of Sentence RepetitionFour repetitions of the word “HAPPY”.
But every time the word is functioning in different ways.

He feels HAPPY.
Others feel HAPPY
He is being forced into happiness (is he actually HAPPY?)
The truth: He is actually not HAPPY at all
